SQL_STMT_U.val: select T0.JOURNAL_DT as 'Tanggal', T0.REF_NO as 'No Referensi', C1.GTSRegNum as 'No.RM', C2.CARDNAME as 'Pembayaran', C1.CARDNAME as 'Nama Pasien', T0.JOURNAL_NO, TX.WhsName as 'Ruangan', T1.ACCOUNT_NO as'No. Perkiraan', T4.AcctName as 'Nama Perkiraan', T1.DEBIT_AMT as 'DEBET', T1.CREDIT_AMT as 'KREDIT', T1.DOC_NO, SUM(T1.DEBIT_AMT - T1.CREDIT_AMT) OVER(ORDER BY REF_NO,T0.JOURNAL_NO, T1.CREDIT_AMT,DOC_NO ) AS BALANCE, T1.KET_DT from GL_JURNALH T0 LEFT JOIN OCRD C1 ON C1.CardCode=t0.CARDCODE LEFT JOIN OCRD C2 ON C1.CardCode=t0.INSUCARD join GL_JURNALD T1 on T0.JOURNAL_NO=T1.JOURNAL_NO JOIN OACT T4 ON T4.AcctCode=t1.ACCOUNT_NO LEFT JOIN OWHS TX ON TX.WhsCode=t1.WHSCODE WHERE T0.JOURNAL_DT between ':1' and ':2' :3 and reverse_no='' AND T0.REF_NO like '%:4%' order by REF_NO,JOURNAL_NO, KREDIT,DOC_NO

select CoId, BplId, Fiscal, Project, Activity, AcctCode, OcrCode, Budget01, Budget02, Budget03,Budget04, Budget05, Budget06, Budget07, Budget08, Budget09, Budget10, Budget11, Budget12, BudgetTotal, Real01, Real02, Real03, Real04, Real05, Real06, Real07, Real08, Real09, Real10, Real11, Real12, RealTotal, CONCAT(STR(ROUND(ISNULL(((RealTotal/NULLIF(BudgetTotal, 0)) * 100), 0), 2), 14, 2), '%') AS PercentTotal, (BudgetTotal-RealTotal) as Remaining from activitybudget_view where CoId=:1 and BplId=:2 and Fiscal=:3 and Activity=:4 and AcctCode=:5 and OcrCode=:6 and Project=:7

select sum(BudgetTotal) as BudgetTotalSum, sum(RealTotal) as RealTotalSum from activitybudget_view where CoId=:1 and BplId=:2 and Fiscal=:3 and Activity=:4 and AcctCode=:5 and OcrCode=:6 and Project=:7

select CoId, BplId, Fiscal, Project, Activity, AcctCode, OcrCode, Budget01, Budget02, Budget03, Budget04, Budget05, Budget06, Budget07, Budget08, Budget09, Budget10, Budget11, Budget12, BudgetTotal, Real01, Real02, Real03, Real04, Real05, Real06, Real07, Real08, Real09, Real10, Real11, Real12, RealTotal from activitytarget_view V where V.CoId=:1 and V.BplId=:2 and V.Fiscal=:3 and V.AcctCode=:4 and V.OcrCode=:5
select sum(BudgetTotal) as BudgetTotalSum , sum(RealTotal) as RealTotalSum from activitytarget_view V where V.CoId=:1 and V.BplId=:2 and V.Fiscal=:3 and V.AcctCode=:4 and V.OcrCode=:5

select B.CO_ID as CoId, L.BplId as BplId, B.Fiscal_Year as Fiscal, '' as Project, ''as Activity, B.ACCOUNT_NO as AcctCode, B.COST_CENTER as OcrCode, isnull(B.BUDGET_1,0) as Budget01, isnull(B.BUDGET_2,0) as Budget02, isnull(B.BUDGET_3,0) as Budget03, isnull(B.BUDGET_4,0) as Budget04, isnull(B.BUDGET_5,0) as Budget05, isnull(B.BUDGET_6,0) as Budget06, isnull(B.BUDGET_7,0) as Budget07, isnull(B.BUDGET_8,0) as Budget08, isnull(B.BUDGET_9,0) as Budget09, isnull(B.BUDGET_10,0) as Budget10, isnull(B.BUDGET_11,0) as Budget11, isnull(B.BUDGET_12,0) as Budget12, isnull(B.BUDGET_YEAR,0) as BudgetTotal, isnull(C.ENDING_01,0) as Real01, isnull(C.ENDING_02,0) as Real02, isnull(C.ENDING_03,0) as Real03, isnull(C.ENDING_04,0) as Real04, isnull(C.ENDING_05,0) as Real05, isnull(C.ENDING_06,0) as Real06, isnull(C.ENDING_07,0) as Real07, isnull(C.ENDING_08,0) as Real08, isnull(C.ENDING_09,0) as Real09, isnull(C.ENDING_10,0) as Real10, isnull(C.ENDING_11,0) as Real11, isnull(C.ENDING_12,0) as Real12, (isnull(C.ENDING_01,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_02,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_03,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_04,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_05,0) +isnull(C.ENDING_06,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_07,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_08,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_09,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_10,0) +isnull(C.ENDING_11,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_12,0)) as RealTotal from GL_BUDGET B left join OBPL L on B.BR_ID = L.RepName left join OACT A on B.ACCOUNT_NO = A.AcctCode left join GL_BALANCE C on B.ACCOUNT_NO = C.ACCOUNT_NO and B.FISCAL_YEAR = C.FISCAL_YEAR and B.BR_ID = C.BR_ID and B.CO_ID = C.CO_ID and isnull(B.COST_CENTER, '') = isnull(C.COST_CENTER,'') where A.ActType = 'R' and B.CO_ID=:1 and L.BplId=:2 and B.FISCAL_YEAR=:3 and B.ACCOUNT_NO=:4 and B.COST_CENTER=:5

select sum(isnull(B.BUDGET_YEAR,0)) as BudgetTotalSum, sum(isnull(C.ENDING_01,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_02,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_03,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_04,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_05,0) +isnull(C.ENDING_06,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_07,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_08,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_09,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_10,0) +isnull(C.ENDING_11,0)+isnull(C.ENDING_12,0)) as RealTotalSum from GL_BUDGET B left join OBPL L on B.BR_ID = L.RepName left join OACT A on B.ACCOUNT_NO = A.AcctCode left join GL_BALANCE C on B.ACCOUNT_NO = C.ACCOUNT_NO and B.FISCAL_YEAR = C.FISCAL_YEAR and B.BR_ID = C.BR_ID and B.CO_ID = C.CO_ID and isnull(B.COST_CENTER, '') = isnull(C.COST_CENTER,'') where A.ActType = 'R' and B.CO_ID=:1 and L.BplId=:2 and B.FISCAL_YEAR=:3 and B.ACCOUNT_NO=:4 and B.COST_CENTER=:5
select * from activitybudget_view where CoId=:1 and BplId=:2 and Fiscal=:3 and Activity=:4 and AcctCode=:5 and OcrCode=:6
select sum(BudgetTotal) as BudgetTotalSum, sum(RealTotal) as RealTotalSum from activitybudget_view where CoId=:1 and BplId=:2 and Fiscal=:3 and Activity=:4 and AcctCode=:5 and OcrCode=:6
